Tajhon WILSON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1550 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 12, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.
